---
title: Beany Zucchini Quesadillas with Lime Crema, Romaine Salad, and Southwestern Spices
description: Cumin and chili powder bring a one-two punch of spice and smokiness to these jam-packed veggie quesadillas. But worry not—the tangy lime crema and refreshingly crisp romaine salad help cool things off. You’ll practice filling and toasting quesadillas until they’re irresistibly warm and melty, then delight as they drip with cheesy goodness in your hands.
